  "title": "USE \u2014 Storage",
  "uid": "use-storage",
  "description": "USE method for storage. Utilization/Saturation/Errors across two confirmed backends: OCP PVCs (kubelet_volume_stats_*, platform prometheus, 31 PVCs) and TrueNAS ZFS (zfs_pool_* / zfs_dataset_*, UWM job=truenas-zfs). GAPS (honest, not invented): (1) democratic-csi volume-count metrics are NOT scraped anywhere \u2014 volume counts here are derived from PVC series presence, not from a CSI exporter. (2) storageclass is NOT a label on kubelet_volume_stats_* and kube_persistentvolumeclaim_info was not confirmed in inventory, so PVCs are grouped by namespace/persistentvolumeclaim/node rather than by storageclass. (3) zfs_* is TrueNAS-host-only (no per-rk8s/OCP breakdown); pools are grouped by the 'pool' label. (4) zfs_pool_health / zfs_pool_fragmentation_ratio value scales are exporter-defined and shown raw \u2014 no semantic mapping is asserted.",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "label": "thanos-querier",
        "hide": 0,
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {}
      },
      {
        "name": "namespace",
        "type": "query",
        "label": "PVC namespace",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
        },
        "definition": "label_values(kubelet_volume_stats_capacity_bytes, namespace)",
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(kubelet_volume_stats_capacity_bytes, namespace)",
          "refId": "namespace"
        },
        "refresh": 2,
        "sort": 1,
        "multi": true,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "pool",
        "type": "query",
        "label": "ZFS pool",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
        },
        "definition": "label_values(zfs_pool_size_bytes, pool)",
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(zfs_pool_size_bytes, pool)",
          "refId": "pool"
        },
        "refresh": 2,
        "sort": 1,
        "multi": true,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
